      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence residuals documented; not required to be formally assessed at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal assessment of numerical solver error beyond residual monitoring is not required. Residuals were monitored and converged to below 1e-5 for all equations, providing baseline confidence without formal assessment."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
