    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis identification for the CPB device. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all evaluated operating points.",
